  <p>
    The Brandbook is Intuo's internal design reference.
    It describes how or when you should choose on of the many design patterns
    to ensure consistency.
  </p>

  <p>
    There's a lot we can improve upon and feedback is always welcome.
    The Brandbook is an ongoing project that evolves naturally with time,
    hence we will occasionally add or remove things.
  </p>

  <h3 class="anchor-container">
