    <a name="dependencies" class="anchor-text"></a>
    Dependencies
  </h3>

  <hr>

  <ul>
    <li>Our styles are built with SCSS.</li>
    <li><a href="https://middlemanapp.com">Middleman</a> is used to serve the GitHub pages.</li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/middleman/middleman-syntax">middleman-syntax</a> for code highlighting.</li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/rails/turbolinks">turbolinks</a> for rapid page loading.</li>
    <li>We use our own Intuo icon font alongside of <a href="ionicons.com">Ionicons</a>.</li>
    <li>Intuo's design framework is built on top of <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap-sass">Bootstrap Sass 3</a>.</li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/ai/autoprefixer-rails">Autoprefixer</a> is used to generate vendor-prefixed declarations.</li>
  </ul>

